Snippet for front matter date:

```bash
---
title: $(1:date '+%A, %d %B, %Y')
date: $(2:date +%Y-%m-%d)
---
```

Yields

```
---
title: Tuesday, 17 May, 2022
date: 2022-05-17
---
```

Doesn't add the ordinal but better than nothing. Assign to tab trigger or shortcut key